# GoldCraft Community License v1.0 #

Copyright (c) 2026 Wa3te4

You're free to:

* View and study the source code.
* Fork the project.
* Modify the code for personal use.
* Learn from it.
* Share improvements and pull requests.

## The one big rule

Don't take significant portions of this project and present them as your own work.

If you use code, systems, assets, or ideas from this project in something public, give credit somewhere reasonable.

A link to the original repository is enough.

## Commercial use

If you want to use substantial parts of Terreria in a commercial project, sell a modified version, or redistribute it as part of another game, please contact me first.

I'm probably cool with it.

Just don't be weird about it.

## No warranty

This project is provided "as is".

If it corrupts your save, crashes your browser, summons bugs, or causes you to fall into lava repeatedly, that's on you.

## In plain English

The code is open.

That doesn't mean you can jack my stuff, remove my name, and call it yours.

Be respectful.
Give credit.
Make cool things.
